    "Id": "chassisdef_cannonade_CN7-R",
    "Name": "Cannonade",
    "Details": "The CN7-R is a 95-ton dedicated fire platform built around a single brutal premise. Three Gauss Rifles and an Ultra AC/5 deliver devastating ballistic output from beyond effective retaliation range. Crawling at 32 kph, it trades all mobility for raw firepower, carrying 8 tons of ammunition to sustain prolonged engagements. With no energy weapons as backup, positioning is everything, but a well-placed CN7-R can dismantle most opposition before they ever close to effective range.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Accurate Weapon - Gauss</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.15</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Lower, Right Lower</color>",
    "Icon": "NEEDS_ICON"
  },
